data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT! LOOK NO FURTHER for your Florida Lifestyle home! Come discover this beautiful home located in Laurel Pines Nokomis.  Well-maintained, two bedrooms, two full bathrooms, an open floorplan layout and cathedral ceilings, this home as wonderful features!  Master bedroom includes walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom, which has been tastefully updated.  French doors open to an over-sized bonus room - big enough for your jam sessions or game room.  Dining room, master bedroom and bonus room overlook the lanai, straight out to meticulously maintained botanical garden in the spacious backyard.  Lovely kitchen includes stainless-steel appliances and spacious pantry, as well as a nook that can be used as a small office space or small dining area. Interior has beautifully-soft natural lighting. Exterior is very well-lit for safety.  The property sits on an over-sized lot in a quiet cul-de-sac.  This location is prime!  Very close to Nokomis beach (within 2 miles!), easy bike ride to the Legacy trail and minutes to dining and shopping!  This home includes accordion hurricane shutters, Kinetico full water softening system, irrigation well with sprinkler system, two-car garage and a large covered and screened lanai with grill area for easy relaxing and outdoor dining.  Entire house was REPLUMBED in 2020.  Small deed-restricted HOA, low fees, no CDD.  Don't wait to call this beauty HOME!
